I shall be forced to leave this country.

122
00:08:15,728 --> 00:08:18,856
Oh, I wish-

123
00:08:18,965 --> 00:08:21,934
Oh, I wish I could have stayed
just one more year or two.

124
00:08:22,034 --> 00:08:26,095
There was so much I wanted to see
and to do and to have done to me.

125
00:08:26,205 --> 00:08:32,075
Oh, my God. I got so swept up in
the scapegoating and fun of Proposition 24...

126
00:08:32,178 --> 00:08:37,047
I never stopped to think it might
affect someone I cared about.

127
00:08:38,651 --> 00:08:41,176
You know what, Apu?

128
00:08:41,287 --> 00:08:44,381
I am really, really
gonna miss you.

129
00:08:58,905 --> 00:09:02,466
You know what really "aggravateses" me
is them "immigants. "

130
00:09:02,575 --> 00:09:05,043
